{
  "family": "EOS S3",
  "description": "QuickLogic EOS S3 \u2014 ARM Cortex-M4F MCU with embedded FPGA (eFPGA) SoC. Simple ordering code format: QL-S3{variant}-{package_grade}{suffix}. QuickLogic has limited public documentation on ordering codes.",
